msgid ""
"Tatra, bhikkhave, yamidaṃ dhammasamādānaṃ paccuppannadukkhañceva āyatiñca "
"dukkhavipākaṃ, taṃ avidvā avijjāgato yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti:"
msgstr ""
"When it comes to the way of taking up practices that is painful now and "
"results in future pain, an ignoramus, without knowing this, doesn’t truly "
"understand:"

msgctxt "mn46:6.2"
msgid ""
"‘idaṃ kho dhammasamādānaṃ paccuppannadukkhañceva āyatiñca dukkhavipākan’ti."
msgstr ""
