msgctxt "mn46:14.1"
msgid ""
"Katamañca, bhikkhave, dhammasamādānaṃ paccuppannadukkhañceva āyatiñca "
"dukkhavipākaṃ?"
msgstr ""
"And what is the way of taking up practices that is painful now and results "
"in future pain?"

msgctxt "mn46:14.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco sahāpi dukkhena sahāpi domanassena pāṇātipātī hoti, "
"pāṇātipātapaccayā ca dukkhaṃ domanassaṃ paṭisaṃvedeti;"
msgstr ""
"It’s when someone in pain and sadness kills living creatures, steals, and "
