msgctxt "mn46:21.5"
msgid ""
"Tassa te pivato ceva chādessati vaṇṇenapi gandhenapi rasenapi, pivitvā ca "
"pana sukhī bhavissasī’ti."
msgstr ""
"If you drink it, the color, aroma, and flavor will be appetizing, and after "
"drinking it you will be happy.’"

msgctxt "mn46:21.6"
msgid "So taṃ paṭisaṅkhāya piveyya, nappaṭinissajjeyya."
msgstr "He wouldn’t reject it. After thinking, he’d drink it."

msgctxt "mn46:21.7"
msgid ""
"Tassa taṃ pivato ceva chādeyya vaṇṇenapi gandhenapi rasenapi, pivitvā ca "
"pana sukhī assa."
msgstr ""
"The color, aroma, and flavor would be appetizing, and after drinking it he "
"would be happy."

msgctxt "mn46:21.8"
msgid ""
"Tathūpamāhaṃ, bhikkhave, imaṃ dhammasamādānaṃ vadāmi, yamidaṃ "
"dhammasamādānaṃ paccuppannasukhañceva āyatiñca sukhavipākaṃ. (4)"
msgstr ""
"This is comparable to the way of taking up practices that is pleasant now "
"and results in future pleasure, I say."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya22"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc21"></a>
msgctxt "mn46:22.1"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, vassānaṃ pacchime māse saradasamaye viddhe "
"vigatavalāhake deve ādicco nabhaṃ abbhussakkamāno sabbaṃ ākāsagataṃ "
"tamagataṃ abhivihacca bhāsate ca tapate ca virocate ca;"
msgstr ""
"It’s like the time after the rainy season when the sky is clear and "
"cloudless. And when the sun rises, it dispels all the darkness from the sky "
"as it shines and glows and radiates."

msgctxt "mn46:22.2"
msgid ""
"evameva kho, bhikkhave, yamidaṃ dhammasamādānaṃ paccuppannasukhañceva "
"āyatiñca sukhavipākaṃ tadaññe puthusamaṇabrāhmaṇaparappavāde abhivihacca "
"bhāsate ca tapate ca virocate cā”ti."
msgstr ""
"In the same way, this way of taking up practices that is pleasant now and "
"results in future pleasure dispels the doctrines of the various other "
"ascetics and brahmins as it shines and glows and radiates.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc22"></a>
msgctxt "mn46:22.3"
msgid "Idamavoca bhagavā."
msgstr "That is what the Buddha said."

msgctxt "mn46:22.4"
msgid "Attamanā te bhikkhū bhagavato bhāsitaṃ abhinandunti."
msgstr "Satisfied, the mendicants were happy with what the Buddha said."

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "mn46:22.5"
msgid "Mahādhammasamādānasuttaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ chaṭṭhaṃ."
msgstr ""
